em Interface! \nCtrl+Arrow Keys - This will move camera one tile at a time! \n1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 0 - The number Keys are for Quickcast! \n    Default is letter a - j in Spell List for 1 - 0. \n    Use the Spell Macro List (F11)To customize! \nScroll Lock - Take a Screenshot to Remember! \nShift+/ or ? - To See Most of this List in Game! \n==================================\nThanks for reading and we hope you enjoy your time spent with us!\n',2,1,16,0,0),(275,'Xevia',0,'Xevia','Newbie','=======\rLevel 5\r=======\r- choose your class\r- take killing quest from npc mayor\r- learn spell as soon as possible\r- do collecting item quest as many as you can\r  ( the reward increase when your level get higher )\r- do gold donation just for unleash first power requirement\r\r\r========\rLevel 25\r========\r- get your unleash first power at your tutor npc\r  ( you will get new weapon and armor )\r- buy mystery box helm, shield, accesory and hand items\r  ( try to get the royal and celestial )\r- do killing quest\r- do collecting items\r- do gold donation just for unleash second power requirement\r- farm items for creation quartz and fox tail\r  ( obsidian, limestone, fox fur, red fox fur)\r\r\r=============\rLevel 30 - 50\r=============\r- take the essence weapon and armor quest\r  ( it will increase your weapon and armor )\r- farm items\r  ( bones, ash, quartz, fox tail )\r- try to enchant your helm, shield, accesory and hand items\r  ( right now the min level for +7 eq is 30 )\r\r\r========\rLevel 50 \r========\r- chat GM you will get free materials to create\r  ( crown / necklace / mantle / boots )\r- try to enchant your helm, shield, accesory and hand items\r  ( right now the min level for +7 eq is 30 )\r\r\r========\rLevel 60\r========\r- get your unleash second power at your tutor npc\r  (it will increase some of your spell damage and reduce the aethers)\r- do killing quest\r  ( start from this level you go to dungeon cave from npc warper ( 52, 57 )\r- do collecting items\r- do gold donation just for unleash third power requirement\r- try to create crown / necklace / mantle / boots\r- farm items for creation quartz and fox tail\r  ( obsidian, limestone, fox fur, red fox fur)\r- try to enchant your helm, shield, accesory and hand items\r  ( right now the min level for +7 eq is 30 )\r\r\r========\rLevel 90\r========\r- get your unleash third power at your tutor npc\r(it will increase some of your spell damage and reduce the aethers)\r\r- do killing quest\r\r- do collecting items\r\r- do gold donation just for unleash third power requirement\r\r- farm items for forging weapon and armor\r( forging weapon and armor can be use at lv 95 )\r( check the requirement items from npc 50,69 and 51, 79)\r\r- farm items for creation\r\r- try to enchant your full equip\r( right now the min level for +7 eq is 30 )\r\r\r========\rLevel 95\r========\r- forge weapon and armor\r\r- farm items for creation or you can buy from mystery box npc\r\r- try to enchant your forge weapon and armor\r( your target is +7 full equip )\r\r\r========\rLevel 99\r========\r- at this state hopefully you already achieve +7 full equip\r\r- if your exp is full you (4294967295) you can sell exp for gold\r\r- you can start the rebirth quest click mayor to see the quest\r\r',3,1,16,0,0),(276,'Leonidas',0,'Leonidas','Controls and Hotkeys','===[ Welcome ]===\n==================================\nHot Keys: \n\nF1 Menu - Character Status Screen, Character Info & Stats, Toggles, and more as added. \nF2 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½Subpath ChatÃ¯Â¿Â½ On/Off! \nF3 - Friends List. Save Player Names Here. \nF4 - Realm Center. Locks/Unlocks Camera. \nF5 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½WhispersÃ¯Â¿Â½ (Private Messages) On / Off! \nF6 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½ShoutsÃ¯Â¿Â½ (Kingdom Messages) On/Off! \nF7, F8 - Turn Volume Up/Down \nF9 - Ignore List. If someone is bothering you add them here. \nF10 - Option Tab to Turn On/Off many Features\nF11 - Spell Macro List. To Set Up Your Spells 1-0. a-j is default \nF12 - Fast Walk On/Off Toggle \nCtrl-R - This will refresh your screen. \nCtrl-W - Opens the User List. Can click on names to Whisper them. \n\nYour Character: \n\ns - Opens your Status Tab! Page Up/Down to See your Legend! \ni - Press i to open your Inventory Tab! Press Again to Expand List! \nShift+= or + - To Open your Spell List! Press Again to Expand List!  \nc - Press c then letter of inventory item then comma then another item.\n     Example: c then a,b Enter. This will swap item a and b in Inventory! \nShift+c or C - Press C then letter of Spell, then comma, then another. \n     Example: C then i,j Enter. This will swap Spells in i and j in Spell List!\n\nPick up, Transfer, Drop: \n\n, - Comma Picks Up One Item Under You and Place it in your Inventory! \nShift+, or . - This will Pick Up ALL Items Under You Place in Inventory! \nCtrl+, - This will Pick Up All Items in all Tile Around You! (9 Tiles) \nh - Hand an item by letter number or Gold with  Key! \nH - Hand ALL of an item by letter or  Gold with  Key! \nd - Drop an Item by letter or Gold with  Key! \nD - Drop all of an Item by letter. View Inventory with ? Key! \n\n==================================\nThanks for reading and we hope you enjoy your time spent with us!\n',1,1,16,0,0),(277,'Leonidas',0,'Leonidas','Welcome!','===[ Welcome ]===\n==================================\nA wonderous world of adventure is ahead of you. \nTo Walk - Use the Arrow Keys, left click, or hold right click. \nTo Attack - Use the Space bar, Auto Attack Spell, or Left Click. \n\nIf you are having issues with NPCs, Mobs, or Items not appearing, please contact a GM or use the helpdesk on the website. \n\nCommunication: \n\nTo Talk - Press the Enter or \' Key. \nShift+\' (Quote) - Then type in the player name, then enter, \nand then type your message and send it with the Enter key. \nWhisper ! to chat with your clan members.\nWhisper !! to chat with your group members.\nWhisper @ to chat with your subpath members.\nWhisper ? to reach out to mentors for help.\nWhisper & to chat with other members looking to hunt (must join hunter list).\n\nShift+1 or ! - To Shout. This reaches further than Normal Talk. \nShift+; or : - Express Emotions. Select a letter and see for yourself. \nb - Opens the Boards to Read and Reply to Forum Threads! \ng - Press g then type in player name and hit enter to Group! \nShift+g - Toggle On/Off your Group. \nm - Press m to Open your personal Mailbox! \n\nCombat: \n\nSpace Bar - Swings your Weapon \nt - Press t then a letter of item in Inventory to Throw It! \nShift+z or Z - Cast a Spell by pressing Z then letter of spell then Enter \n         Example: Z then s Enter. This casts spell in s slot from Spell Book!\ne - Eat an Item by pressing e, then letter of food in Inventory! \nu - Use an item by pressing u then letter of item in Inventory! \nw or Shift+w or W - Wield any Equipment in Inventory by letter! \nT - Take off item by Prompt in chat window. You can also \n        remove items from status screen by double clicking! \n\nMiscellaneous: \n\n/ping - check on your connection status! \n/played - See how long youve been playing for! \nShift+Q or Alt-X - To Close Out and Leave the Game! \nr - Can be used to Ride wild Horses! \no - Press o to Open Doors and Interact with Objects! \nShift+E - Toggles On/Off Exchange Feature! \nf - Opens the Group Tab to see your Party! \nShift+i or I - Opens the Creation System Interface! \nCtrl+Arrow Keys - This will move camera one tile at a time! \n1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 0 - The number Keys are for Quickcast! \n    Default is letter a - j in Spell List for 1 - 0. \n    Use the Spell Macro List (F11)To customize! \nScroll Lock - Take a Screenshot to Remember! \nShift+/ or ? - To See Most of this List in Game! \n==================================\nThanks for reading and we hope you enjoy your time spent with us!\n',2,1,16,0,0),(278,'cedric',0,'cedric','Controls and Hotkeys','===[ Welcome ]===\n==================================\nHot Keys: \n\nF1 Menu - Ch