udah subpath baru damage swing kepake bngt\r\rnanti kalau ol kabarin aja yak\rkita coba bareng',6,1,19,0,0),(311,'Ruble',0,'cornel','Triple slash and swing damage','> barusan gw coba kalau damage triple slash itu\r> (currentHealth + currentMagic) * damageFactor + 250\r> \r> jadi kalau hp dan mp makin dikit damage nya makin berkurang\r> \r> nah damagefactor itu nambah saat naik level dan  kelar quest > unleash\r> \r> jadi makin tinggi level dan kelar quest unleash damage spell > jadi nambah jg\r> \r> \r> kalau untuk swing barusan gw coba damage nya nambha\" aja\r> pengkali nya sama jg\r> makin tinggi level dan kelar quest unleash pengkali damage > swing nambah jg\r> \r> tapi buat awal\" swing blom kepake bngt\r> nanti pas udah subpath baru damage swing kepake bngt\r> \r> nanti kalau ol kabarin aja yak\r> kita coba bareng\r\roh.. ternyata mirip atknya rogue yah, terbiasanya sama vita atk warrior soalny :D\rpantes turunnya banyak soalny buffnya warrior pake mana gede sih 10k gt klo gk salah\r\ryang swing ak gk pake lagi sih soalnya pake triple slash mulu, td it kebetulan sekalian tes damagenya karena ada vampiric aura.\r\rheal dari vampiric aura lumayan sih 50% dari damage gt yh\r\ranyway thank you yah',21,1,19,0,0),(312,'cornel',0,'Ruble','wokeh','> > barusan gw coba kalau damage triple slash itu\r> > (currentHealth + currentMagic) * damageFactor + 250\r> > \r> > jadi kalau hp dan mp makin dikit damage nya makin berkurang\r> > \r> > nah damagefactor itu nambah saat naik level dan  kelar quest > > unleash\r> > \r> > jadi makin tinggi level dan kelar quest unleash damage spell > > jadi nambah jg\r> > \r> > \r> > kalau untuk swing barusan gw coba damage nya nambha\" aja\r> > pengkali nya sama jg\r> > makin tinggi level dan kelar quest unleash pengkali damage > > swing nambah jg\r> > \r> > tapi buat awal\" swing blom kepake bngt\r> > nanti pas udah subpath baru damage swing kepake bngt\r> > \r> > nanti kalau ol kabarin aja yak\r> > kita coba bareng\r> \r> oh.. ternyata mirip atknya rogue yah, terbiasanya sama vita > atk warrior soalny :D\r> pantes turunnya banyak soalny buffnya warrior pake mana gede > sih 10k gt klo gk salah\r> \r> yang swing ak gk pake lagi sih soalnya pake triple slash mulu, > td it kebetulan sekalian tes damagenya karena ada vampiric > aura.\r> \r> heal dari vampiric aura lumayan sih 50% dari damage gt yh\r> \r> anyway thank you yah\r\r\rwokeh siap',7,1,19,0,0),(313,'Makayla',0,'Makayla','Controls and Hotkeys','===[ Welcome ]===\n==================================\nHot Keys: \n\nF1 Menu - Character Status Screen, Character Info & Stats, Toggles, and more as added. \nF2 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½Subpath ChatÃ¯Â¿Â½ On/Off! \nF3 - Friends List. Save Player Names Here. \nF4 - Realm Center. Locks/Unlocks Camera. \nF5 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½WhispersÃ¯Â¿Â½ (Private Messages) On / Off! \nF6 - Turn Ã¯Â¿Â½ShoutsÃ¯Â¿Â½ (Kingdom Messages) On/Off! \nF7, F8 - Turn Volume Up/Down \nF9 - Ignore List. If someone is bothering you add them here. \nF10 - Option Tab to Turn On/Off many Features\nF11 - Spell Macro List. To Set Up Your Spells 1-0. a-j is default \nF12 - Fast Walk On/Off Toggle \nCtrl-R - This will refresh your screen. \nCtrl-W - Opens the User List. Can click on names to Whisper them. \n\nYour Character: \n\ns - Opens your Status Tab! Page Up/Down to See your Legend! \ni - Press i to open your Inventory Tab! Press Again to Expand List! \nShift+= or + - To Open your Spell List! Press Again to Expand List!  \nc - Press c then letter of inventory item then comma then another item.\n     Example: c then a,b Enter. This will swap item a and b in Inventory! \nShift+c or C - Press C then letter of Spell, then comma, then another. \n     Example: C then i,j Enter. This will swap Spells in i and j in Spell List!\n\nPick up, Transfer, Drop: \n\n, - Comma Picks Up One Item Under You and Place it in your Inventory! \nShift+, or . - This will Pick Up ALL Items Under You Place in Inventory! \nCtrl+, - This will Pick Up All Items in all Tile Around You! (