ahead of you. \nTo Walk - Use the Arrow Keys, left click, or hold right click. \nTo Attack - Use the Space bar, Auto Attack Spell, or Left Click. \n\nIf you are having issues with NPCs, Mobs, or Items not appearing, please contact a GM or use the helpdesk on the website. \n\nCommunication: \n\nTo Talk - Press the Enter or \' Key. \nShift+\' (Quote) - Then type in the player name, then enter, \nand then type your message and send it with the Enter key. \nWhisper ! to chat with your clan members.\nWhisper !! to chat with your group members.\nWhisper @ to chat with your subpath members.\nWhisper ? to reach out to mentors for help.\nWhisper & to chat with other members looking to hunt (must join hunter list).\n\nShift+1 or ! - To Shout. This reaches further than Normal Talk. \nShift+; or : - Express Emotions. Select a letter and see for yourself. \nb - Opens the Boards to Read and Reply to Forum Threads! \ng - Press g then type in player name and hit enter to Group! \nShift+g - Toggle On/Off your Group. \nm - Press m to Open your personal Mailbox! \n\nCombat: \n\nSpace Bar - Swings your Weapon \nt - Press t then a letter of item in Inventory to Throw It! \nShift+z or Z - Cast a Spell by pressing Z then letter of spell then Enter \n         Example: Z then s Enter. This casts spell in s slot from Spell Book!\ne - Eat an Item by pressing e, then letter of food in Inventory! \nu - Use an item by pressing u then letter of item in Inventory! \nw or Shift+w or W - Wield any Equipment in Inventory by letter! \nT - Take off item by Prompt in chat window. You can also \n        remove items from status screen by double clicking! \n\nMiscellaneous: \n\n/ping - check on your connection status! \n/played - See how long youve been playing for! \nShift+Q or Alt-X - To Close Out and Leave the Game! \nr - Can be used to Ride wild Horses! \no - Press o to Open Doors and Interact with Objects! \nShift+E - Toggles On/Off Exchange Feature! \nf - Opens the Group Tab to see your Party! \nShift+i or I - Opens the Creation System Interface! \nCtrl+Arrow Keys - This will move camera one tile at a time! \n1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 0 - The number Keys are for Quickcast! \n    Default is letter a - j in Spell List for 1 - 0. \n    Use the Spell Macro List (F11)To customize! \nScroll Lock - Take a Screenshot to Remember! \nShift+/ or ? - To See Most of this List in Game! \n==================================\nThanks for reading and we hope you enjoy your time spent with us!\n',2,1,26,0,0),(418,'JinFish',0,'Basbus','Rebirth','10 Animal essence\r10 warior Essence\r10 Rogue Essen\r10 Poet essence\r10 mage essence\r800K gold',4,1,27,0,0),(419,'JinFish',0,'Basbus','Item Broken Armor','kordinat 084/073\r\rRoom 1 Drop \r\rBroken Black Turtle Armor\r\r\rRoom 2 Drop\r\rBroken red Phoenix Armor\r\rRoom 3 Drop\r\rBroken Dragon Armor\r\rRoom 4 Drop\r\rBroken White Tiger Armor\r\r\rMasing2 Butuh 100 Piece untuk SUphat\r\rjadi mending nyari ini dulu baru fokus Leveling',5,1,27,0,0),(420,'JinFish',0,'Basbus','makro Mudah ','https://www.mediafire.com/file/zpw6d17weide3l4/MozToolX-Lite.100330.7z?fbclid=IwAR3pncLK4EPK8GBWqANjaAvSWTDFcgO8DGV1mCrOB_SQi22X8TC3NyFEyLk',6,1,27,0,0),(421,'basbus',0,'JinFish','basbus','N/a/u/r/a/1\r\rn besar om\r',6,1,27,0,0),(422,'SaKuRaGiSr',0,'cornel','craft donation','Om, mau tanya.. untuk craft donation ini..\rkalau sudah donasi 501 kan dapat dari seal fixed 800\runtuk pembuatan pure nya sndiri bagaimana..? \rmengikuti atau tetap tentative dapatnya?',44,1,27,0,0),(423,'cornel',0,'SaKuRaGiSr','re','> Om, mau tanya.. untuk craft donation ini..\r> kalau sudah donasi 501 kan dapat dari seal fixed 800\r> untuk pembuatan pure nya sndiri bagaimana..? \r> mengikuti atau tetap tentative dapatnya?\r\roh iya lupa di post brubah jg kok bntr yak',7,1,27,0,0),(424,'Colburn',0,'Colburn','Controls and Hotkeys','===[ Welcome ]===\n==================================\nHot Keys: \n\nF1 Menu - Character Status Screen, Character Info & Stats, Toggles, and more as add