er & to chat with other members looking to hunt (must join hunter list).\n\nShift+1 or ! - To Shout. This reaches further than Normal Talk. \nShift+; or : - Express Emotions. Select a letter and see for yourself. \nb - Opens the Boards to Read and Reply to Forum Threads! \ng - Press g then type in player name and hit enter to Group! \nShift+g - Toggle On/Off your Group. \nm - Press m to Open your personal Mailbox! \n\nCombat: \n\nSpace Bar - Swings your Weapon \nt - Press t then a letter of item in Inventory to Throw It! \nShift+z or Z - Cast a Spell by pressing Z then letter of spell then Enter \n         Example: Z then s Enter. This casts spell in s slot from Spell Book!\ne - Eat an Item by pressing e, then letter of food in Inventory! \nu - Use an item by pressing u then letter of item in Inventory! \nw or Shift+w or W - Wield any Equipment in Inventory by letter! \nT - Take off item by Prompt in chat window. You can also \n        remove items from status screen by double clicking! \n\nMiscellaneous: \n\n/ping - check on your connection status! \n/played - See how long youve been playing for! \nShift+Q or Alt-X - To Close Out and Leave the Game! \nr - Can be used to Ride wild Horses! \no - Press o to Open Doors and Interact with Objects! \nShift+E - Toggles On/Off Exchange Feature! \nf - Opens the Group Tab to see your Party! \nShift+i or I - Opens the Creation System Interface! \nCtrl+Arrow Keys - This will move camera one tile at a time! \n1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 0 - The number Keys are for Quickcast! \n    Default is letter a - j in Spell List for 1 - 0. \n    Use the Spell Macro List (F11)To customize! \nScroll Lock - Take a Screenshot to Remember! \nShift+/ or ? - To See Most of this List in Game! \n==================================\nThanks for reading and we hope you enjoy your time spent with us!\n',2,2,3,0,1),(498,'caucibai',0,'cornel','imbalance','Gw selama ini sengaja ga liat2 subpath laen, pengen nostalgia game mmo pertama gw 20+ lalu, \r\rtapi tadi ketemu player poet grinding bareng\rMage kalah damage+kalah area of effect sama poet\rMage udah full+7, mp uda mentok, 10jam grinding lagi jadi mage PERTAMA mentok di server\rKalah sama\rPoet blom full+7 equipnya, mp belom mentok, JARANG grinding exp pulak\r\rOk, gw positif thinking Subpath tertentu, menonjol di bidang lainMythic misalnya, bisa crowd control, makes bossing ez\rTapi buat apa? Gold gw masih sisa 500jt+, itu pun udah gw bagi2+ bantu peer gw, ga kepake\rBoss raid? Ga bisa di para\rAnother angle, skill aoe nya mythic, no cooldown, tapi terbatas areanya kecil, \rDAN ada maksimum input yg bisa di terima sama server, jadi seberapa banyak pun yang mythic teken, akan tetep kalah sama itu poet. Imba\rItu baru dari pov mage, belum dari poet - naturalistYang literally kepake cuman SC nya, healer? Ga kepake, subpath lain punya somekind of self sustain?di sisi lain healer itu sendiri ga punya skill damage yg reliable kayak subpath lain. Imba\rKalo emang begini, hasil grinding manual gw percuma dan ga akan bisa keep up sama subpath laen\rImbalance kills the game itself',51,2,3,0,0),(499,'caucibai',0,'caucibai','[To cornel] imbalance','Gw selama ini sengaja ga liat2 subpath laen, pengen nostalgia game mmo pertama gw 20+ lalu, \r\rtapi tadi ketemu player poet grinding bareng\rMage kalah damage+kalah area of effect sama poet\rMage udah full+7, mp uda mentok, 10jam grinding lagi jadi mage PERTAMA mentok di server\rKalah sama\rPoet blom full+7 equipnya, mp belom mentok, JARANG grinding exp pulak\r\rOk, gw positif thinking Subpath tertentu, menonjol di bidang lainMythic misalnya, bisa crowd control, makes bossing ez\rTapi buat apa? Gold gw masih sisa 500jt+, itu pun udah gw bagi2+ bantu peer gw, ga kepake\rBoss raid? Ga bisa di para\rAnother angle, skill aoe nya mythic, no cooldown, tapi terbatas areanya kecil, \rDAN ada maksimum input yg bisa di terima sama server, jadi seberapa banyak pun yang mythic teken, akan tetep kalah sama itu poet. Imba\rItu baru dari pov mage, belum dari poet - naturalistYang literally kepake cuman SC nya, healer? Ga kepake, subpath lain punya somekind of self sustain?di sisi lain healer itu sendiri ga punya skill damage yg reliable kayak subpath lain. Imba\rKalo emang begini, hasil grinding manual gw percuma dan ga akan bisa keep up sama subpath laen\rImbalance kills the game itself',9,2,3,0,0),(500,'cornel',0,'caucibai','re','> Gw selama ini sengaja ga liat2 subpath laen, pengen nostalgia > game mmo pertama gw 20+ lalu, \r> \r> tapi tadi ketemu player poet grinding bareng\r> Mage kalah damage+kalah area of effect sama poet\r> Mage udah full+7, mp uda mentok, 10jam grinding lagi jadi mage > PERTAMA mentok di server\r> Kalah sama\r> Poet blom full+7 equipnya, mp belom mentok, JARANG grinding > exp pulak\r> \r> Ok, gw positif thinking Subpath tertentu, menonjol di bidang > lainMythic misalnya, bisa crowd control, makes bossing ez\r> Tapi buat apa? Gold gw masih sisa 500jt+, itu pun udah gw > bagi2+ bantu peer gw, ga kepake\r> Boss raid? Ga bisa di para\r> Another angle, skill aoe nya mythic, no cooldown, tapi > terbatas areanya kecil, \r> DAN ada maksimum input yg bisa di terima sama server, jadi > seberapa banyak pun yang mythic teken, akan tetep kalah sama itu > poet. Imba\r> Itu baru dari pov mage, belum dari poet - naturalistYang > literally kepake cuman SC nya, healer? Ga kepake, subpath lain > punya somekind of self sustain?di sisi lain healer itu sendiri > ga punya skill damage yg reliable kayak subpath lain. Imba\r> Kalo emang begini, hasil grinding manual gw percuma dan ga > akan bisa keep up sama subpath laen\r> Imbalance kills the game itself\r\r\rseperti yang gw udah pernah bilang di game dan di group wa\rsemua spell itu masih penyesuaian\rgak mungkin gw kerjain 1 hari kelar\r\rkarna waktu gw ngoding pasti di malem hari\rbesok lanjut kerja lagi masuk kantor\r\r\rdan ini makan waktu paling lama karna 1 subpath gw ubah\rgw harus tes ke 7 subpath lain \r\r\r',10,2,3,0,0),(501,'XnX',0,'XnX','Co